export const GET_INVENTORY='GET_INVENTORY'; // dispatch this action type if we get the inventory list
export const CREATE_INVENTORY='CREATE_INVENTORY'; // dispatch this action type if the inventory was successfully created
export const UPDATE_INVENTORY='UPDATE_INVENTORY'; // dispatch this action type of the inventory is successfully updated
export const DELETE_INVENTORY='DELETE_INVENTORY'; // dispatch this action type if the inventory is successfully deleted
